Package: syntheticdid
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast estimators for Difference-in-Differences (DID), Synthetic Control (SC),
    and Synthetic DiD (SDID). Core numerical routines are implemented in C++ via RcppArmadillo
    with optional OpenMP parallelization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.12), stats, utils
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: data.table, Matrix, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: C++17, OpenMP (optional)
